{"tid":1785551,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"9.5億唔益藍店 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-12-16T12:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T12:55:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"68d8b3cf6d4bf3be2073e8325323b6ce186173ac","tid":1785551,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:47:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191216/20825686/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191216%2F20825686%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7ogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=0ab29cfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191216%2F20825686%2F&h=854ab29f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191216/20825686/</a><br />\n<br />\n9.5億唔益藍店 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191216/large/1576396216_21ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191216%2Flarge%2F1576396216_21ee.jpg&h=e367e8ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民&times;聯策劃打大老細荷包，養住落選區會的一班敗將，據聞四年的包養費要一億五，暫時未有闊佬肯開水喉。一億五雞碎咁多，相對1.1萬黑警半年來OT補水9.5億，九牛一毛。放1.6萬個TG，1.1萬黑警平均每人放超過一個，拎到9.5億，足以日日海底撈飯，幫這家紅色上市公司更上一層天台！歡呼要為周梓樂同學之死開香檳慶祝的黑警，領到九億加班費後，盡情飲到暴斃！未死的話進駐寶福山，日日巡查往返致祭的市民，凡黑衣者，必搜！擾民嗎？受人錢財，瞄準寶福山放TG，二噁英毒量遠比焚香燒冥鏹低嘛，羅致光，對不對？<br />\n<br />\n一邊食蕉一邊扮鬼臉舉中指的執勤黑警，拿九億補水，天方夜譚？喔，草「管」人命的四點鐘警謊又試噏錯，應該學林奠那句：天公地義。九億發下來，交通燈繼續搵便衣砸，裝修商鋪，照計補水，冇理由停。自製炸彈郵包送去年輕人屋企，就算對方唔收，照拉！成功爭取過年前拉夠一萬人！721晚，拍晒白衫鄉黑膊頭唔理元朗站市民死活的黑警，拎住八萬銀補水，跟劉蛇返大灣區消費，寧呃五毛like，唔益撐警藍店；藍店冚家拎。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"33f987766871f22be3886686da47339c996aeb90","tid":1785551,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:48:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PY03AQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPY03AQa.jpg&h=511bc04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-2.xx&amp;oh=f485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a&amp;oe=5EAED219\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-sin2-2.xx%26oh%3Df485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a%26oe%3D5EAED219&h=70a59658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad486331efe01780d9ab44ab6ff5b4d2c88bdc05","tid":1785551,"uid":65178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:55:10.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母 唔該同黑警曱甴割蓆<br />\n呢班撚樣狗閪要一世俾香港人睇唔起<br />\n邊個唔杯黑警 我哋都應該好似藍絲咁標籤佢"}]}